+/**
+ * Provides support for the conversion of moodle1 backup to the moodle2 format
+ *
+ * @package    mod
+ * @subpackage ouwiki
+ * @copyright  2011 Mark Nielsen <mark@moodlerooms.com>
+ * @license    http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html GNU GPL v3 or later
